description:
The goal of the game is simple - deliver various cargo to the desired point and complete tasks. But be extremely careful - the load may be unstable and fragile!

The game has many different tasks with different levels of difficulty - from the simplest with light and small loads to complex with bulky and fragile loads.

Plunge into a real challenge for fans of work transport simulators and transport all the cargo!

GAME FEATURES:
- Realistic physics and forklift control system;
- Lots of different tasks;
- Many different types of cargo;
- Realistic sounds;
